LabeledForm
===========

Introduction goes here.


Todo
=======
Make grouping customizable

Example
=======

labeled_form_for object do |form|
	form.text_field :name
	form.submit "Please save"
end

Produces:
<form ...>
  <p>
    <label title="Name" for="object_name"/>
    <input type="text" value="My Name" name="object[name]" id="object_name">
  </p>
  <p>
    <input type="submit" value="Please save" id="object_name">
  </p>
</form>


